              "elType": "widget",
              "settings": {
                "html": "\n\n<nav class=\"nav\" role=\"navigation\">\n  <div class=\"nav__inner\">\n    <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"nav__logo\"><img src=\"03_compact_dark.svg\" alt=\"Veredian\" height=\"40\"></a>\n    <div class=\"nav__links\">\n      <a href=\"products.html\">Products</a><a href=\"technology.html\">Technology</a><a href=\"markets.html\">Markets</a><a href=\"company.html\">Company</a><a href=\"investors.html\" class=\"active text-teal\">Investors</a><a href=\"news.html\">News</a><a href=\"careers.html\">Careers</a><a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"nav__actions\">\n      <button class=\"nav__lang\">EN | AR</button>\n      <a href=\"deck-request.html\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">REQUEST BRIEFING</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</nav>\n\n<section class=\"hero hero--short\">\n  <div class=\"container hero__inner hero__inner--centered\">\n    <div class=\"hero__content\">\n      <p class=\"eyebrow text-teal\">INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY</p>\n      <h1 class=\"text-white\">Sovereign Silicon Platform. Series A.</h1>\n      <p class=\"hero__subtitle text-silver\">Veredian is building a portfolio of sovereign semiconductor platforms for governments that cannot accept foreign supply-chain risk — beginning with EDGE-VISION™ 1000, the flagship edge AI vision SoC.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section section--white\">\n  <div class=\"container text-center\">\n    <div class=\"section__header\">\n      <h2>Why This Investment Is Structurally Different</h2>\n      <p>Veredian is not a single-product bet. It is a sovereign silicon platform — one IP foundation, a family of products, and a category where the buyer is a national government and the moat is structural.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"grid grid--2\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\n      <div class=\"card card--challenge\">\n        <div class=\"card__icon-wrap\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path></svg></div>\n        <h3 class=\"card__title\">Sovereign IP Structure</h3>\n        <p class=\"card__body\">All programme IP is assigned to a nationally incorporated entity at formation. The IP cannot be acquired, restricted, or revoked by any foreign entity.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"card card--challenge\">\n        <div class=\"card__icon-wrap\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div>\n        <h3 class=\"card__title\">Platform Economics</h3>\n        <p class=\"card__body\">One IP foundation carries the entire portfolio — every new product and custom programme compounds on silicon already built and audited.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"card card--challenge\">\n        <div class=\"card__icon-wrap\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M21.21 15.89A10 10 0 1 1 8 2.83M22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2v10z\"></path></svg></div>\n        <h3 class=\"card__title\">Non-Discretionary Revenue</h3>\n        <p class=\"card__body\">The annual compliance subscription is tied to national CIP certification law. Revenue grows automatically with the installed base.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"card card--challenge\">\n        <div class=\"card__icon-wrap\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"></path><polyline points=\"22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01\"></polyline></svg></div>\n        <h3 class=\"card__title\">Strategic Exit Channels</h3>\n        <p class=\"card__body\">A sovereign silicon platform creates M&A optionality with defence primes, national technology champions, and infrastructure acquirers.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section section--light\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section__header text-center\">\n      <h2>How the Programme Is Structured</h2>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"platform-compare\" style=\"margin-top:0;\">\n      <div class=\"compare-box\" style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #E2E8F0;\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-teal\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Series A</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-weight: 700; color: #1E293B; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size:13px;\">Flagship to EVT silicon</p>\n        <p style=\"color: #64748B; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;\">Architecture freeze / RTL maturity / GDS sign-off / EDGE-VISION™ 1000 EVT + pilots</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"compare-box\" style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #E2E8F0;\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-teal\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Series B</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-weight: 700; color: #1E293B; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size:13px;\">Production + portfolio scale</p>\n        <p style=\"color: #64748B; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;\">Triggered by: EVT validated + first programme revenue / EDGE-SENSE™ definition complete</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"compare-box\" style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #E2E8F0;\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-teal\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Profitability</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-weight: 700; color: #1E293B; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size:13px;\">Post-production</p>\n        <p style=\"color: #64748B; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;\">Chip revenue + compliance subscriptions + custom programmes compound across the portfolio</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section section--navy text-center\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-white\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">Request the Investment Briefing</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-silver\" style=\"margin-bottom: 40px; max-width:700px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;\">Full portfolio overview, technical architecture, market analysis, and financial model — available to qualified sovereign investors under NDA. Response within one business day.</p>\n    <a href=\"deck-request.html\" class=\"btn btn--primary\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">REQUEST BRIEFING</a>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: var(--silver);\">Direct enquiries: <a href=\"mailto:investors@veredian.ai\" class=\"text-teal\">investors@veredian.ai</a></p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<footer class=\"footer\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"footer__grid\">\n      <div class=\"footer__brand\">\n        <img src=\"03_compact_dark.svg\" alt=\"Veredian\" height=\"36\">\n        <p class=\"footer__tagline\" style=\"margin-top:24px;color:#A8B4C0;font-size:12px;\">Sovereign Silicon. Designed for Nations.<br>© 2026 Veredian. All rights reserved.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer__nav\">\n        <p class=\"footer__links-title\">PAGES</p>\n        <div class=\"footer__links\">\n          <a href=\"products.html\">Products</a>\n          <a href=\"technology.html\">Technology</a>\n          <a href=\"markets.html\">Markets</a>\n          <a href=\"company.html\">Company</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer__nav\">\n        <p class=\"footer__links-title\">COMPANY</p>\n        <div class=\"footer__links\">\n          <a href=\"investors.html\">Investors</a>\n          <a href=\"news.html\">News</a>\n          <a href=\"careers.html\">Careers</a>\n          <a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer__offices\">\n        <p class=\"footer__offices-title\">CONTACT</p>\n        <div class=\"footer__office\">\n          <p class=\"footer__office-label\" style=\"color:var(--silver);\">Middle East HQ<br>Engineering Centre</p>\n          <a href=\"mailto:hello@veredian.ai\" class=\"text-teal\" style=\"display:block;margin-top:8px;\">hello@veredian.ai</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer__legal\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);margin-top:80px;\">\n      <p>This website is provided for informational purposes only and does not constitute an offer or solicitation of any securities in any jurisdiction. Qualified investors and programme partners only.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n"
